data.description: Here is your exclusive opportunity to own one of the select few homes over 2200 sqft in Hawks Preserve that gracefully adjoins the lush preserve. Discover the ultimate retreat in this stunning 4-bedroom + Den home that seamlessly merges contemporary elegance with the serene beauty of nature. Enjoy an abundance of premium upgrades, along with a freshly installed roof in July 2023 and a 2020 AC System, ensuring not only peace of mind with reduced maintenance and insurance expenses but also a significant boost to the property's overall value. Another major upgrade includes a paved driveway and an expansive lanai, plus a custom-built pet crate in the laundry area that ensures your furry friend has a cozy and personalized space. This modern home also boasts built-in ceiling speakers in the living area, creating an immersive audio experience. Experience the enchantment of a serene paradise as you surround yourself with nature's beauty, abundant wildlife, and your very own private outdoor garden oasis, where lush greenery and vibrant blooms create an exclusive retreat. Seize this unique opportunity to make it yours!
